        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>Readying Elders and Americans with Disabilities Inclusively for Disasters Act or the READI for Disaster Act</b></p> <p>This bill establishes a series of programs and requirements relating to disaster preparedness for individuals with disabilities and the elderly, including grant programs and a national commission.</p>]]></text>
